CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 16, 1964, pg. A2 reads: "HCIA Target - The Homewood Community Improvement Association (HCIA) is driving in Homewood-Brushton to eliminate garages violating zoning ordinances. An HCIA spokesman pointed out that this establishment at 7409 Frankstown Ave., adds to the deterioration of the community and destroys the property value of the adjacent and neighboring properties. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Stanley's Bar and Grill, 7403 Frankstown Avenue, with Joe Vilsack Auto Service at 7409 Frankstown Avenue, and houses on street, Homewood
